A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
Cross Domain Tactical OPIR Processing delivers a mechanism providing reach-back support for battlespace awareness functions and manages the timely transfer of
newly developed tools to operational users.

 This program element may include necessary civilian pay expenses required to manage, execute, and deliver weapon system capability. The use of such programs
 funds would be in addition to the civilian pay expenses budgeted in program element 0605827F, 0605828F, 0605829F, 0605831F, 0605832F, 0605833F, 0605898F,
 0606398F. In FY24 2.01 million was expended for civilian pay expenses in this program element, and in FY25 3.64 million is forecasted for civilian pay expenses in this
 program element.

