Title: Component-level Operational Decision Advantage                                                                                    1.851       0.000              -
Description: Component-level Air Forces (AFFOR) Command and Control and processes for full-spectrum competition
against high end adversaries. CODA will leverage prior AFRL research, organizational development techniques, and state
